ğŸ” Step 1: Create IAM Role for EC2

Go to:

AWS Console â†’ IAM â†’ Roles â†’ Create Role

Attach policies:

AmazonS3ReadOnlyAccess

CloudWatchReadOnlyAccess

Attach this role to your EC2 instance.

ğŸ–¥ Step 2: Launch EC2

